    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Aasimar&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Darkvision&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Some aasimars possess the ability to manifest halos. An aasimar with this racial trait can create <i>light </i>centered on her head at will as a spell-like ability. When using her halo, she gains a +2 circumstance bonus on Intimidate checks against evil creatures and on saving throws against becoming blinded or dazzled. This racial trait replaces the darkvision racial trait.</p>",
